tid":2458439,"uid":74339,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T12:44:05.000Z","msg":"好多人曲解佢嘅說話 佢原本係覺得記者呢個專業係好重要 直到721後開始改變 到自己企喺庭上嘅被告席嘅時候 佢已經過渡到認為做一個真正嘅自己先係對抗政治審判嘅最好辦法<br />\n<br />\n個人意見 有錯請補充或指正"},{"pid":"02e959c93aa5e23e6880ab96291375a1dfe06aac","tid":2458439,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T12:51:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faeaa0e312b489c9aba0fa2cdce7a073c5f04963","tid":2458439,"uid":192409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T12:52:37.000Z","msg":"破左局未?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955564bc8bdaa726008f0043ba649e61f71add4e","tid":2458439,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T13:00:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7617144edb71c86247c9ff85b4f61ed6d83eaf4f","tid":2458439,"uid":64092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T13:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0e97ed321bf30cc95da3a48260c7d026164819","tid":2458439,"uid":335924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T13:10:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8d71c0672d06e5f2bf4ba295fab8cc26373e97","tid":2458439,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c